  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <title>KosJourney Notification</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <style>
      body {background-color:#ffffff;font-size:12px;}
      table.white {background-color:#ffffff;}
      h1 {margin-bottom: 2px; margin-left:63px;}
      h2 {margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 2px;}
      h3 {margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 2px;}
      h4 {margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 2px;}
      h5 {margin-top: 4px;margin-bottom: 0px;}
      div {margin-top: 0px;}
      a {margin-top:0px;border: none;text-decoration: none;}
    </style>
    <table style="width: 600px;" align="center" bgcolor="#ffffff"  cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td style="width: 600px;" width="600">
            <!-- Main Content Area --> 
            <table style="width: 600px; background: #ffffff;" bgcolor="#ffffff" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td style="width: 600px;" width="600">
                    <h1 style="font-family: helvetica,arial,sans-serif; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 100; color: #000000; font-size: 33px; line-height: 33px; text-align: center">Ko's Journey<br />
                      <span style="font-size: 34px; color: #000000; font-weight:600;">We have a newly updated site!</span>          
                    </h1>
                    <img style="border: none; margin-top: 20px;" src="http://dl.dropbox.com/u/3105141/C2CDN/Ko/graphics/email/purple_splat.png" width="628" height="20" />
                  </td>
                </tr> 
              </tbody>
            </table>
            <!-- end Banner --> 

            <!-- Content Area--> 
            <table style="width: 600px;" align="center" bgcolor="#fefefe" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <table style="width: 600px; margin-top: 2px;" align="center" bgcolor="#fefefe" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                      <tbody>
                        <tr>
                          <td>
                            <p style="font-family: helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 25px; margin-right: 50px; margin-left: 40px; color: #5f6062">
                              Hello <%= @teacher.name %>,
                            </p>
                            <p style="font-family: helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 25px; margin-right: 50px; margin-left: 40px; color: #5f6062">
                              We have exciting news! KO's Journey has a brand new site. We have recently upgraded our web framework to help offer our customers a better experience. We added new video upload features for teachers and students. Our game now delivers from a speedy CDN network for faster game load times. We also added a new even more secure authentication system. 
                            </p>
                            <p style="font-family: helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 25px; margin-right: 50px; margin-left: 40px; color: #5f6062">
                            	As part of this system, we needed to reset some passwords to allow for the better encryption. If you go to login and find you are unable, please follow the steps listed below.
                            </p>
                            <ul style="font-family: helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 25px; margin-right: 50px; margin-left: 40px; color: #5f6062">
                              <li>1. Make sure you are on the Teacher Login. When you go to the login page the inital form is for students. There is a link at the top of the login box that says Teacher Login. Click this and the form will update for teachers.</li>
                              <li>2. If your password that you know is not working. Please use "kosjourney". Once you login you'll be met with a password update form to change your password. Please do so, then the next time you go to login you'll be able to use your newly created and better encrypted password.</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p style="font-family: helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 25px; margin-right: 50px; margin-left: 40px; color: #5f6062">
                              Thank you,
                              The Imagine Education Team.
                            </p>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </tbody>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
<!-- end Content Area -->
          </td>
        </tr>
